oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: 5th Annual Woodstick
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Hank Flamingo (Musical group); Woodcuts (prints); Baseball; Viceroys (Musical group);
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Three color window card (blue, red, and black on white) announcing the 5th Annual Woodstick featuring Hank Flamingo, The Viceroys, Scull Soup, L.I.F.E., The Clintons, Jimmie D. and the B-Movie Blues, Rob Peter, Topay Paul, Bleu Cheese, Super Drag, Bleu Jackson, and The Rude Street Peters at the Dallas Ricker Complex in Fall Branch, Tennessee on July 29. Poster features a woodcut of a baseball player.
